# Folder Structure

```
idea8/
├── backend/    # FastAPI app, DB models, routers, services, scripts
├── frontend/   # React app, UI components, pages, hooks, contexts
├── website/    # Next.js marketing site (optional)
├── docker-compose.yml, .env, start.sh  # Orchestration & config
```

- **backend/app/**: Main FastAPI app, routers, schemas, services, models
- **backend/scripts/**: DB migrations, seeders, utilities
- **frontend/src/components/**: Modular React UI components (shadcn/ui, custom)
- **frontend/src/pages/**: Main app pages (Dashboard, Profile, Settings, etc.)
- **frontend/src/contexts/**: React Context API for state (e.g., Auth)
- **frontend/src/hooks/**: Custom React hooks
- **frontend/src/lib/**: API utilities, helpers
- **website/src/app/**: Next.js marketing/landing page
